<plot>Martin, a succesful consultant, is investigating a case of mismanagement at a Dutch municipality. In his private life things are not that well though. He has suspicions that his girlfriend Carina is cheating on him. Also he gets stalked by a certain Frits Bleekemolen. When Martin finally agrees to an interview with him, all he gets are awkward questions about his personal situation and he throws him out of the house. Frits doesn't give up though, and confronts Martin again. When he finds out Carina took Frits on a cleaning job he loses his temper. Martin tries to cover up the evidence, a decision he will regret.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?671118</url></doc>
